title: #92Noon! Montage/Birk&Siny/Bercich/TheDrive/Lavelle
description: Montage to start for a winless Vikings team, some calls/talkers, then a combo of Matt Birk and Dave Sinykin to end the first hour. Pete Bercich in for two segments, a new bit called "The Drive" that chronicles the most impactful(or fateful) drive of the Vikes game, then Lavelle in to finish the show!
